CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 26, 1955, pg. 10 reads: "Girl Friends Talk It Over - Other members of the National Girl Friends who came to Pittsburgh last week-end to attend an executive board meeting got together to talk it over. Standing are Lillian Gregory and Louise Kent of Cleveland.  Seated: Margo Dison, Eleanor Sutler, Ruth Clement and Cecelia Ward, all of Cleveland, and Norma Simmons of Albany, N.Y. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Girl Friends Inc. members, standing includes Lillian Gregory and Louise Kent; seated from left: Margo Dison, Eleanor Sutler, Ruth Clement, Cecelia Ward, and Norma Simmons; gathered in interior with square patterned room dividers
